abstract: Tristane Banon, French writer who accused Dominique Strauss-Kahn of trying to rape her in 2003, says she will not pursue civil case against him.
snippet: Tristane Banon, the French writer who accused Dominique Strauss-Kahn of trying to rape her eight years ago, said she would not pursue a civil case against him.
lead_paragraph: Tristane Banon, the French writer who accused Dominique Strauss-Kahn of trying to rape her eight years ago, said she would not pursue a civil case against him.

headline.main: France: Writer Says She Won’t Sue Strauss-Khan
